ELBEY PROJECTS — Website Blueprint & Build Plan
Big decision (I picked one so you don’t stall)

Recommendation: Build with WordPress + Elementor (or a lightweight theme) + managed hosting (affordable, reliable).
Why: cheapest to launch, easiest for the customer to update, huge plugin ecosystem for booking/SEO/analytics, and simple maintenance path. If you want a prettier no-code handoff and don’t mind higher monthly costs, Webflow is the alternative — great design control but pricier.
