## **1. WordPress + Elementor Starter Outline**

### **Homepage Layout (Elementor Sections)**

1. **Hero Section**

   * Full-width background: red muscle car / garage shot
   * H1: *Elbey Projects — Honest mobile mechanics & engine service in [CITY]*
   * H2 subhead: *Fast diagnostics • Mobile repairs • 15 years of hands-on experience*
   * Primary CTA: Button → anchor to Booking Form
   * Optional: small secondary CTA → Gallery

2. **Why Us**

   * 3 columns: Icon + short line (Price / Honest / Mobile & Reliable)
   * Quick hover animation

3. **Top Services Preview**

   * 3–5 cards (Brakes, Oil, Suspension, Diagnostics, Mobile Repair)
   * Each card: image + 1 line description + “Book Now” button (anchor to form)

4. **Booking Widget / Form**

   * Name, Phone, Email (optional)
   * Service dropdown (Maintenance, Engine, Transmission, Suspension, Brakes, Diagnostics, Mobile Repair, Inspections)
   * Preferred date + time
   * Vehicle make/model/year
   * Address or pickup/dropoff info
   * Short notes
   * Attach photo (optional)
   * “How did you hear about us?” dropdown
   * Consent checkbox
   * Submit → email + Zapier webhook → SMS confirmation + calendar invite

5. **Gallery Highlight**

   * Carousel: before/after + 1 video thumbnail
   * CTA: “View Full Portfolio”

6. **Testimonials**

   * 3–5 reviews, star rating
   * Optional: slider effect

7. **About Snippet**

   * 50–70 words + link → full About page

8. **Local SEO Block**

   * Service areas + Google Business Profile snapshot

9. **Footer**

   * Contact: phone/email
   * Social links
   * Quick nav
   * Hours (24/7)

---

### **Pages & Structure**

* **About:** 350–600 words, emphasize Saudi experience, hands-on expertise, mobile & honest approach
* **Services:** Each service: 300–450 words, 3 images, CTA to booking form
* **Gallery:** Visual-first, captions + context lines
* **Testimonials:** Pull from Google Reviews / client quotes
* **Blog:** Future SEO tool (600–1200 words each, conversational, local keywords)
* **Shop:** Future, Stripe/Square integration
* **FAQ / Policies:** Pricing logic, turnaround, T&Cs

---

### **2. Elementor & Plugin Setup**

* **Plugins:**

  * Elementor Pro (visual builder + forms)
  * WPForms / Elementor Forms (for booking)
  * RankMath / Yoast SEO
  * UpdraftPlus (backups)
  * WP Rocket or LiteSpeed (cache)
  * Optional: Instagram feed / YouTube embed
* **Zapier Workflow:**

  * Form submission → email + SMS → Google Calendar event
  * SMS template: *“Hi [Name], your booking for [Service] on [Date] is confirmed. – Elbey Projects”*

---

### **3. Hosting & Domain**

* **Budget:** Hostinger Managed WP
* **Standard Pro:** SiteGround Managed WP
* SSL: free via Let’s Encrypt
* DNS configured → domain + Google Business Profile

---

### **4. Local SEO / Launch Checklist**

* Google Business Profile: photos, hours, categories
* NAP consistency
* Service-area pages
* Local schema: LocalBusiness + Service
* Blog: 1–2 posts/week first month
* Review solicitation after each job

---

### **5. Visual Style**

* Colors: Black / Charcoal bg, Red #c62828 accents, Cream/Ivory text
* Fonts: Bold condensed sans-serif headlines, clean sans body
* Media: Before/after shots, action shots, 30–60s video clips

